Class CountingUtils

java.lang.Object
org.krmdemo.techlabs.core.utils.CountingUtils
public class CountingUtils extends Object
Utility-Class to build a counting-map from the Stream of any objects that have properly implemented Object.equals(Object) and Object.hashCode() (and for sorted counting-maps).
